Who sought out Eileen Gray and became an important patron of her work for the Salon des Artistes Decorateurs?<image 1>

A. Le destin screen
B. Jacques Doucet
C. Salon des Artistes Decorateurs
D. Eileen Gray

B. Jacques Doucet

Jacques Doucet was an important patron of Eileen Gray's work for the Salon des Artistes Decorateurs.
